    KRAFT_NAME: "Ulyana Kraft",
    KRAFT_DESCR:
      "<p>«Art is an integral part of my life for me. It in any of its manifestations helps to learn to look at the world through the eyes of another person who created the art. Any kind of art - intellectual or decorative - stimulates thought, develops imagination and observation. I am very glad that nowadays creative people are reaching a new level and doing cool projects not only in the real, but also in the virtual world!»</p>",
