    TKACH_META_DESCRIPTION: "",
    TKACH_NAME: "Artyom Tkach",
    TKACH_POSITION: "Digital Artist",
    TKACH_ABOUT:
      '<p>Participated in the festival of contemporary ethnic arts "Stereotypes of the Future" as an art director, and exhibited his interactive AR-art at the Street Art Museum in St. Petersburg, in November 2019. <br> Made an AR-project for a joint exhibitions of the Hermitage and the British Museum, the first exhibition of the art of ancient Assyria in the history of Russia - “I erected my royal palace there.”</p><p>He promoted the NFT community of Russia in the international NFT space, increased the recognition of Russian digital artists. Invented and organized the first in the CIS NFT-collaboration of 42 artists, the final canvas of which was sold for 8.4 ETH (≈ $ 30,000).</p><p>Exhibited his NFT-art at the exhibition of the SOVRISK project #flood in Underground Zaryadye Museum.</p><p>He is one of the administrators of Adobe After Effects, the largest community of CG specialists in the CIS. Actively participates in the formation and development of the community of digital artists, both informationally and financially, I provide support to novice artists.</p>',
    TKACH_WORK_1_TITLE: "WHO ARE YOU?",
    TKACH_WORK_1_DESCR:
      '"Hiding his face behind a mask of letters, drowning in confident brush sections as in memory, where the past is in eternal conflict with the future."',
    TKACH_WORK_1_TXT:
      "<p>Beauty is a relative concept. But there are rules and laws that can be controlled: harmony of color, composition, its rhythm and dynamics.</p><p>Light waves by themselves have no color. Color arises only when these waves are perceived by the human eye and the brain.</p><p>Speaking about color harmony, people rely on subjective feelings, while the concept of color harmony is an objective law.</p>",
    TKACH_WORK_2_TITLE: "Minotaur",
    TKACH_WORK_2_TXT:
      "<p>“The labyrinth is a symbol of the brain. The Minotaur is the animal part of the mind, and Theseus is the human part. The animal part is stronger, but the human part wins in the end. This is the meaning of the history of evolution.</p><p>Maybe this is the whole point. Not to think where the way out is, but to understand that life is a crossroads on which you are standing right now. Then the labyrinth will disappear - after all, it exists only in our minds, but in reality there is only a simple choice - where to go. ”</p>",
    TKACH_WORK_3_TITLE: "Darkness",
    TKACH_WORK_3_TXT:
      "<p>“If you find yourself in the dark and see at least the faintest ray of light, you should go to it, instead of reasoning whether it makes sense to do it or not. <br>Maybe it really doesn't make sense. But just sitting in the dark doesn't make sense anyway. ”</p>",

    ODINTRI_DESCR:
      "<p>ODINTRI has been engaged in graphic design for a long time, comprehended the art of calligraphy and lettering and eventually became a prominent representative of the calligraffiti trend.</p>\n" +
      "        <p>Maestro works with Latin letters, Cyrillic and even Arabic script! In addition to Moscow and St. Petersburg, Ruslan distinguished himself with his works in Barcelona and Dubai.</p>\n" +
      "        <p>This is the case when a person does not paint canvases, but lives them: ODINTRI is in a mode of constant self-improvement, is fond of the exact sciences and, frankly, amazes us with the symbiosis of his life philosophy and self-realization in art.</p>",
